The hierachical description of the 2-stage shift register
is here
	shift_reg_2.hsys

The make-file to build the VHDL model of shift_reg_2 is
here
	Makefile

This make-file is called from the build.sh at the shift_reg_4
level.

The VHDL code for the shift_reg_2 entity is kept in this 
directory
	vhdl/

The description of the 1-stage shift register is in this
directory
	shift_reg_1/
